      "description": "Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Flawless interior. Full service history included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    }
  ],
